---
import Typography from '~components/ui/Typography.astro';
import ConfidenceChart from '~assets/illustrations/confidence-chart.svg';
import Radar from '~assets/illustrations/radar.png';
import Integrations from '~assets/illustrations/integrations.png';
---

<div class="container">
  <div class="title">
    <Typography tag="h2" styling="headingM" align="center">
      Automated QA on autopilot <br />omoka finds the bugs, you just get the
      tickets
    </Typography>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="item">
      <div class="leftSide">
        <Typography tag="h3" styling="headingM" align="left">
          Zero effort testing
        </Typography>

        <Typography tag="p" styling="paragraphL" align="left" color="gray300">
          Letâ€™s be honest - no one likes testing their own app. It is boring,
          time-consuming, and costly. The AI agent for testing is always on
          standby to handle the process, so you can focus on scaling your
          business knowing your app works perfectly.
        </Typography>
      </div>

      <div class="rightSide confidenceChart">
        <ConfidenceChart />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <div class="leftSide">
        <Typography tag="h3" styling="headingM" align="left">
          Is your app bug free right now?
        </Typography>

        <Typography tag="p" styling="paragraphL" align="left" color="gray300">
          You only get one chance to make a first impression. When users see a
          bug, whether big or small, they stop trusting you. Your brand looks
          unprofessional and your credibility disappears. omoka protects your
          reputation before it is too late.
        </Typography>
      </div>

      <div class="rightSide radar">
        <img src={Radar.src} alt="Radar" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <div class="leftSide">
        <Typography tag="h3" styling="headingM" align="left">
          Bugs land in your backlog
        </Typography>

        <Typography tag="p" styling="paragraphL" align="left" color="gray300">
          Don't waste a second manually creating tickets and remove the worst
          testing part. omoka sends precise evidence straight to Jira or any
          tool you use. No manual typing, no "how to reproduce" calls. Just a
          clear list of what to fix - it's that simple.
        </Typography>
      </div>

      <div class="rightSide integrations">
        <img src={Integrations.src} alt="Radar" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style lang="scss">
  @use '~styles/mixins/media' as *;

  .container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
    border-left: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
  }

  .title {
    width: 100%;
    padding: var(--s-40);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
  }

  .content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .item {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-800);

    @include media-min('md') {
      flex-direction: row;
      height: 300px;
    }
  }

  .leftSide {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--s-36);

    width: 100%;
    padding: var(--s-40);
  }

  .rightSide {
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;

    width: 100%;
    padding: var(--s-24);

    @include media-min('md') {
      position: relative;

      align-items: end;
      justify-content: end;

      height: 100%;
      padding: 0;
    }
  }

  .confidenceChart {
    display: none;

    /* stylelint-disable-next-line selector-pseudo-class-no-unknown */
    :global(svg) {
      transform: translateY(40px) translateX(8%);
      scale: 0.9;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }

    @include media-min('md') {
      display: block;
    }
  }

  .radar {
    position: relative;
    display: none;
    height: 100%;

    img {
      position: absolute;
      transform: translateY(50%) translateX(5%) scale(1.6);

      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;

      object-fit: contain;
    }

    @include media-min('md') {
      display: block;
    }
  }

  .integrations {
    display: none;

    img {
      transform: translateY(-5.5%) translateX(5%);
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    @include media-min('md') {
      display: block;
    }
  }
</style>
